			         <para>
               <para.body>Find the maximal subset <math>
                     <latex>D</latex>
                  </math> of <math>
                     <latex>\RNr</latex>
                  </math> on which the expression below determines a function <math>
                     <latex>D\to \RNr</latex>
                  </math>.</para.body>
            </para>
		       </problem.body>
      </problem>
		    <part.exercise>
